In old age, the mind is the main instrument to attain enlightenment. Vairag is developed.
<br>Q: How does devotion relate to this? A lot of older people are very devotional.
<br>A: Devotion is emotional state. It&#8217;s either tantra or bhakti. It&#8217;s also state of vairag. Surrender to God. <span class=date>9/21/80</span>
